f5fc82ec2e3c7f80fb516ebf5a43f14977028f","tid":1646556,"uid":18730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eebc5424cc35c5ddddd35ffcc1aa9dc3bb27f450","tid":1646556,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T11:31:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護前線 刻不容緩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人，我哋眾籌咗好多次，賣廣告、出書、拍電影&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n但係最重要嘅，係買裝備保護前線!!!!<br />\n而唔係等佢哋受傷咗之後先去支援佢地!!!<br />\n<br />\n請大家快啲支持YHF！過咗一日，先得十幾人支持，好傷心<br />\n係，我無Fact check，但係我情願相信，呢個世界有人願意冒被捕風險，都要做眾籌<br />\n希望大家衡量過後，可以支持做實事嘅團隊。<br />\n運動未完，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸贏都好，保護手足應該係和理非最需要關心嘅事。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1643523/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1643523/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/payments/?oid=1662043&amp;err=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fpayments%2F%3Foid%3D1662043%26err%3D1&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcpqf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=ea7ce455\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/payments/?oid=1662043&amp;err=1</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TJhHcCt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJhHcCt.jpg&h=5bcbfa54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a0b315c3e1a53267218fc715a253cc5dc02847b","tid":1646556,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"deba09a9f9016f0d390959a5659bdd6fa0777d77","tid":1646556,"uid":149008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T11:40:10.000Z","msg":"寧鳴而死"},{"pid":"730507325ef342881f4a1daa8fc8be737956b842","tid":1646556,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"【行動】SUCK小隊 10.13『 罷鷲 』行動 + 香城online 【冒險者公會】計劃<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/ekOckT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank